Package cz.vse.java.util.observerDP

Interface ISubject

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AGeneralService, AService, C2RConnection, C2SConnection, Client, ClientServiceManagement, OrderManagement, Router, S2CConnection, S2RConnection, Server, ServiceClientsManagement, SRCContainer, Storage, StorageService, TaskContainer, TaskManagement
    public interface ISubject

    The interface of ISubject is used to contain all methods of the type to be overriden (implemented).

    This interface defines the Subject from Observer design pattern. This side of the relation has to be able to add IObserver, to remove it and to notify all the observers.

    Written for project "Connections2".
    Version:
    05. 04. 2020
    Author:
    Vojtěch Pavlů
